{"tid":2148749,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"為愛妻號伯伯寫的歌【如常】- 謝芊彤 Chintung Tse","createTime":"2020-08-10T05:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:35:01.000Z","uid":198,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bafdacfa1c6c81ea97b60fe0574a4d1676bb7e69","tid":2148749,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=11&amp;v=s-WgJbuiKwI&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D11%26v%3Ds-WgJbuiKwI%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YqDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=1307ec83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=11&amp;v=s-WgJbuiKwI&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n昨天分享了網友創作的歌曲《如常》<br />\n然後主角愛妻號伯伯的家人聽到<br />\n原創者感到很欣慰<br />\n香港依然充滿好人好事<br />\n即使不談政治也可以很#connected<br />\n大家努力<br />\n<br />\n▶️ 這是創作人的原訊息：<br />\n沈教授你好，我是謝芊彤，一個獨立唱作人，那天看你分享了愛妻號伯伯的報導，傷心又感動，所以為這個故事寫了一首歌【如常】，想和你分享。一直相信音樂能將故事和感情好好紀錄並傳得更遠，希望可以將伯伯的感情好好存放在這首歌中，並且不要對新聞上的死亡數字麻木，因為每個數字背後都是一個活生生的人，他們都是因為政府失效的施政而喪命香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n▶️ 附上是加拿大多倫多電台朋友獲知故事後，今早的電台分享<br />\n▶️【如常】謝芊彤<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-WgJbuiKwI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-WgJbuiKwI&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YqDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=9f5c165b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-WgJbuiKwI</a><br />\n<br />\n如常掛念<br />\n如常痴痴的想你<br />\n願每日能見到你<br />\n眉宇裡感覺你悲喜<br />\n<br />\n如常到達<br />\n如常走廊中等你<br />\n與你談談天氣<br />\n惹你生氣<br />\n只要共你一起<br />\n<br />\n如常見面 如常凝望你<br />\n想輕撫你的皺紋 親你的額頭<br />\n緊握你雙手<br />\n如常的一天 如常與你道別<br />\n近又遠如隔幾千里 這厚玻璃<br />\n揮揮手遠去 永遠告別你<br />\n<br />\n▶️ 立場新聞報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/他不是-1487-是享年-88-歲的愛妻號伯伯/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-1487-%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B4-88-%E6%AD%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E5%A6%BB%E8%99%9F%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YqDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=5eb88a11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-1487-%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B4-88-%E6%AD%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E5%A6%BB%E8%99%9F%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF%2F&h=f9b3788a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/他不是-1487-是享年-88-歲的愛妻號伯伯/</a>"},{"pid":"94f64d2a8053f8f9f1285f311c7b11f66b31da57","tid":2148749,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170240053fd91bbc71aa9261088fe20d990f210e","tid":2148749,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bf11ffb825a24cc6c2d601d740a0b80ac5f2e6","tid":2148749,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38be232e80eafe4dbe6b700c7be6a296238ea5a2","tid":2148749,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"